{"arkId":"cl010099523","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099523","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Pot \u00e0 confiture couvert et son plateau lob\u00e9, d\u00e9cor polychrome","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Pot \u00e0 confiture couvert et son plateau lob\u00e9, d\u00e9cor polychrome"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1765","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1765,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"},{"label":"M\u00e9r\u00e9aud, Pierre-Antoine","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"?","dates":[{"date":"vers 1735","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1791","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"M\u00e9r\u00e9aud, Charles-Louis","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"?","dates":[{"date":"1735","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1780","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7210","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"confiturier","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Petit pot et plateau en porcelaine tendre. Le pot \u00e0 panse verticale et arrondie par le bas, porte un couvercle surmont\u00e9 d\u0027une fleur en relief ; et serti d\u0027une monture d\u0027argent \u00e0 festons et agrafes. Le plateau est ovale et \u00e0 lobes. Fond blanc ; contre-fond bleu vermicul\u00e9 d\u0027or. D\u00e9cor \u0022mosa\u00efqu\u00e9\u0022 peint en couleur : des doubles cartouches \u00e0 fond bleu p\u00e2le quadrill\u00e9 et violet avec points d\u0027or et rosettes bleues, alternant avec des cartouches isol\u00e9s violets pointill\u00e9s d\u0027or avec oeils de perdrix r\u00e9serv\u00e9s ; le tout encadr\u00e9 de rinceaux d\u0027or auxquels sont suspendues des guirlandes de feuilles vertes avec petits fruits rouges. Sur le couvercle du pot, une fleur en relief dor\u00e9. Sur le bord du couvercle, une monture en argent dor\u00e9 et cisel\u00e9 d\u0027une frise de festons ajour\u00e9s, avec deux fleurons en relief.","inscriptions":"Marque de l\u0027atelier : \r ; marque de potier sous couverte : S10 (?) (sous le plateau)\r ; marque de S\u00e8vres en bleu, sur couverte ; lettre-date M ; surmont\u00e9 d\u0027une virgule (sigle de M\u00e9reaud jeune) (sous le pot et sous le plateau)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,8","displayDimension":"7,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"17,3","displayDimension":"17,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"13,5","displayDimension":"13,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,5","displayDimension":"4,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5,7","displayDimension":"5,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,8","displayDimension":"2,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,2","displayDimension":"6,2 c